==Stadiums==
{{Cite section|date=October 2025}}
{{Main|Estádio da Várzea|Estádio Nacional de Cabo Verde}}

The national team played at Estádio da Várzea in [[Praia]], on [[Santiago, Cape Verde|Santiago Island]]. The stadium reopened in 2006 and has a capacity of 8,000.

Currently, the team plays the majority of its home matches at the Estádio Nacional de Cabo Verde. The ''Tubarões Azuis'' matches have also been held at the 5,000-seat [[Estádio Municipal Adérito Sena|Adérito Sena Municipal Stadium]] in [[Mindelo]].

